<p><b>Personal Expenses</b></p>




<ul type="discd"><li>Personal insurance</li><li>Personal toiletry items</li><li>Personal medicine kit</li></ul>




<p><b>Meals Not Included</b></p>




<ul type="discd"><li><b>Day 1:</b><span>&nbsp;</span>Breakfast &amp; lunch en route to base camp</li><li><b>Day 6:</b><span>&nbsp;</span>Lunch &amp; dinner during return journey</li></ul>




<p><b>Mandatory Documents</b></p>




<ul type="discd"><li>Medical fitness certificate (to be submitted before trek)</li><li>Original government ID card or valid VISA (mandatory for forest permit entry)</li></ul>




<p><b>Optional Services</b></p>




<ul type="discd"><li>Offloading charge: ₹800 per bag per day<br /><i>(To be paid directly at Govindghat if you choose not to carry your backpack)</i></li></ul>




<p><b>Foreign Nationals</b></p>




<ul type="discd"><li>Additional ₹1600 for trekking permit</li><li>Passport and valid Visa are mandatory</li></ul>




<p>&nbsp;</p>    <h3 class="Inclusionsdetails" style="border-bottom:2px solid #ff4300;">Important Note</h3>
    <p>


<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta name="ProgId" content="Word.DocumentW" />
